{"tid":2360990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普料出席邊境圍牆峻工儀式　或是國會衝突後首露面","createTime":"2021-01-10T09:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:26:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa1d9af652f08cfb8858f7e91148e3664276718","tid":2360990,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569647-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569647-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=228f027f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569647-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a34374c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569647-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮表示，總統特朗普預計星期二前往美國得州接壤墨西哥邊境，出席完成修建400英哩圍牆的儀式，顯示政府致力打擊非法移民的決心，如果行程屬實，很可能是特朗普自國會山莊衝突以來，首次公開露面。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普競逐2016年大選時，提出要在美墨邊境興建圍牆，以堵截非法移民入境，又承諾會由墨西哥支付費用，但報道指，實際上是由美國納稅人付費。"},{"pid":"2cf3c9b23a2bcf1e39cbb023bf74db2bb6cf91c2","tid":2360990,"uid":110568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"老母畀咗1皮我買iPhone, 跟住去咗買iPhone, 結論係我畀錢買iPhone"}]}